reviewText: Part of a group of Christmas gifts, so we have not opened them, but gave 5 stars for the super fast delivery.

What can I say?  Corneil & Bernie is a really great show: smart, witty and oh, so cute.  You just want to reach into the TV and grab that adorable, little dog and smother him with kisses!  It's no wonder you can't find the show on TV any longer...the quality kid shows usually get upstaged by mindless trash.
